Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.99,0:00:21.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to try and gather\Nthe unrestrained winds
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.54,0:00:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll run toward the horizon,\Nalongside the wave crests
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.29,0:00:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ve made my decision,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.99,0:00:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even if there’s a long way to go\Non that road.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.58,0:00:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll continue towards the future I’ve planned
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.08,0:00:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time rushes us\NThe heartbeat speeds up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.20,0:00:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke in the middle of a dream\NI kept searching for that same light
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.29,0:01:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under the shining star-lit sky with\Ncountless constellations and shadows
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.33,0:01:15.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something beyond that…\NWhat were you gazing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.25,0:01:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you gazing at?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.00,0:01:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess the storm is\Ngoing to come soon…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s hurry and head back\Nto the curry shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.66,0:01:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.33,0:01:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That thunder right now…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.50,0:01:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,came from the direction\Nof the Katabami Gold Mine…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.33,0:02:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raiga's Counterattack
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.41,0:02:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-Boss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wake up, Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking around.\NI’m not laughing…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.99,0:02:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey…Ranmaru…!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.12,0:02:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You… What did you do\Nto Ranmaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.41,0:02:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! He…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.99,0:02:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Ranmaru held your hand…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.25,0:03:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you revived and…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.50,0:03:03.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then…Ranmaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.62,0:03:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ranmaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Raiga up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must stop him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.83,0:04:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.62,0:04:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you…that brat’s comrade…?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:12.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it’s a wooden weapon, then…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.54,0:05:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can’t hold it over my head…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.99,0:05:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You little fly…!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.12,0:06:11.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit buzzing!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.00,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m…not smart, you know…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.62,0:06:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.66,0:06:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t know why this happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.41,0:06:43.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, whose fault is it? Yours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.33,0:06:45.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No! That’s not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.99,0:06:48.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps…the guys from the Leaf…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.33,0:06:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah…\Nlf they didn’t come,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.99,0:06:56.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then Ranmaru and I would\Nhave been together forever…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.99,0:06:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.99,0:07:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, don’t you?!\Nlf you don’t know, I’ll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.00,0:07:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.08,0:07:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take me…where they are…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.66,0:07:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Ranmaru.\NFor your funeral…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.99,0:07:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll offer up their corpses for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ranmaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.83,0:08:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This child… Did he give up his life\Nin order to revive Raiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.08,0:08:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rai…ga… Rai…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.58,0:08:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ranmaru! You're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:18.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there! Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.99,0:08:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started raining.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.20,0:09:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we’re almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.79,0:09:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, I’m happy that\Nyou all did this much for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.58,0:09:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Something horrible happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my… What happened, Karashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.54,0:09:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenten is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.79,0:09:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Tenten?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She…fell from a cliff and..
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.91,0:09:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.16,0:09:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was running with her and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:37.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenten said that she would train me\Nin place of Lee…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.91,0:09:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there…when we were\Napproaching the Lightning Pass,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.62,0:09:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the lightning struck and\Na tree came falling and
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:47.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenten fell from the Pass\Nto the bottom of the cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.12,0:09:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! Then you must go\Nhelp her out immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.45,0:09:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go to help, Tenten!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.99,0:09:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:10:01.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm… No, I will…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will come after you guys\Nwith the first-aid kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.08,0:10:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.00,0:10:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go, Naruto, Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,– Yes! 					– Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, Karashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.41,0:10:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, we’re running away\Nfrom here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, child?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:24.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.08,0:10:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll explain it later,\Nso hurry up and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.87,0:10:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will wait at the Lightning Pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.99,0:10:36.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring them for sure. If not…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.41,0:10:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll offer up you and your mom’s corpses\Nto Ranmaru…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.37,0:10:48.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.37,0:10:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don’t want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.99,0:10:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to wait\Nuntil everybody comes back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.83,0:10:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! You are so stubborn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.33,0:11:08.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think that Tenten would\Nfall off a cliff
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.04,0:11:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,merely because of the thunder?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.12,0:11:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.99,0:11:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Karashi…\Nlt seems like he wasn’t trained enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.41,0:11:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.25,0:11:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps…it’s some kind\Nof trap again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or he’s been threatened\Nby someone…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.99,0:11:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the Kurosuki Family is…!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.16,0:11:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe my eyes were cloudy…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:28.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.75,0:11:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s him…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.45,0:11:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He’s burning up with fever…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.99,0:11:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raiga…?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.87,0:11:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He revived, so you should too…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.75,0:11:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s all right. I’m going to die\Nsoon anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.50,0:12:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way! I’m not going to let you say\Nthat you're going to die so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people who were killed by you\Nand Raiga died against their will!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.12,0:12:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not going to let it go your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.99,0:12:17.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of those\Nwhose freedoms you took away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.79,0:12:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m going to have you\Ntake responsibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The storm… It’ll be dangerous\Nto stay here…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.07,0:12:33.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To Grandma’s place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’ve come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raiga!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.19,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.32,0:12:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I’ll take you down for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.53,0:12:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.32,0:13:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That’s not good! Lee!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you…?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.57,0:13:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s in a whole different level\Nfrom before…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.11,0:13:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably that attack was\Nlightning made of Chakra.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.90,0:13:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this one…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:33.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Real lightning is used as the source…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.19,0:13:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he can utilize the power of nature,\Nunlike Chakra, he’ll have no limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.45,0:13:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Byakugan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.95,0:13:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we dodge through\Nthe electric shock and
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.82,0:14:01.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,take this to a close-range battle…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.49,0:14:04.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.19,0:14:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.49,0:14:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:35.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.03,0:14:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.74,0:14:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.65,0:14:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shadow Clone Jutsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:47.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Naruto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.32,0:14:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gentle Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.53,0:14:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You brats! Is that all you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unlike the natural thunder power\NI’m using,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.15,0:15:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chakra has its limits!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.24,0:15:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh…?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You’re an idiot!\NThere’s an idiot here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.49,0:15:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you say to an opponent\Nwho fought with all his power?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time I’m not going to\Nhave a funeral for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.19,0:15:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please Mom, come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.65,0:16:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There’s no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.03,0:16:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I’m going to stay here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Tenten!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.32,0:16:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my! This stupid son of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.19,0:16:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn’t help it,\Nbecause the boss came back to life…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we stay here,\Nwe’re going to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.15,0:16:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only choice we have\Nis to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.78,0:16:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to run away,\Nthen go.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.20,0:16:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not running away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.86,0:16:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m not going to give up,\NI will save this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.15,0:16:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will feed this boy\Nthe curry of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.70,0:16:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.53,0:16:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s the curry that revived Lee.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.95,0:16:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.86,0:17:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything happens,\Nit’s not my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:19.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.28,0:17:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.95,0:17:23.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two… One, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.45,0:17:25.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One, two… One, two…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.78,0:17:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.19,0:17:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is really bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.57,0:18:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this…you’ll feel better.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.99,0:18:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.11,0:18:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You messed up on\Nmixing the spices.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.40,0:18:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.90,0:18:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karashi, could you have memorized\Nmy recipe of the curry of life?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.61,0:19:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Karashi…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the true curry of life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.90,0:19:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, please eat this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can’t even eat\Nif you’re not with Raiga?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.19,0:19:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why…for a person like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.36,0:19:31.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does one need a reason\Nto save someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.70,0:19:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To save you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.24,0:19:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandma Sansho and Karashi\Ndid their best to make the curry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.19,0:19:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t you feel anything seeing\Nthose two trying their best?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.19,0:19:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don’t feel anything,\Nyou’re a horrible human being!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human beings support each other\Nin order to live…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are people who need help,\Ndon’t others naturally lend them a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.03,0:19:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn’t that being human?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.11,0:20:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, one bite is fine.\NWhy don’t you try it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.07,0:20:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what it feels like to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.82,0:20:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raiga …
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.65,0:20:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want him to eat this curry too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.70,0:20:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.70,0:21:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’m far from finished…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.82,0:21:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy…\NWhat is up with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.65,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So many things happen\Non this endless road, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.19,0:21:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although you’re strong-willed,\Nyour voice wavered on the phone today
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.15,0:22:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What dreams did you chase to get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.15,0:22:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even I have times when\NI just don’t understand, baby
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.11,0:22:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you’re sad, I’ll be close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.49,0:22:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even on nights when we’re apart,\NI’ll be close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:45.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll be close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.19,0:22:55.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! What in the world\Nhappened to my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is pitch black in front of me,\Nmy entire body is numb,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.78,0:23:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my body doesn’t do\Nwhat I want it to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.19,0:23:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this feeling…?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.65,0:23:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It’s warm, my entire body\Nis burning,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.99,0:23:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and what is this taste that brings energy\Nup from the bottom of my stomach…?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.65,0:23:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Run! The Curry of Life!
